OL,5, This Morning presenter Alison Hammond  
OL,6, has broken down live on the programme  
OL,7, while reacting to the departure of     
OL,8, ex-colleague Phillip Schofield.        
OL,10,FSchofield told the BBC he feels his    
OL,11,F"career is over" following the affair  
OL,12,Fhe had with a young male colleague.    
OL,14,FSpeaking on Friday's show, Hammond said
OL,15,Fhe had apologised and urged people not 
OL,16,Fto judge his actions too harshly.      
OL,18,F"I'm just finding it really painful    
OL,19,Fbecause obviously I loved Phillip      
OL,20,FSchofield," she said.                  
